  - orderName: Captured Tiles
    tutorialText:
    - Nice job on capturing your first set of tiles
    - The bigger you expand the longer it takes to fill.
    - Try capturing more than 150 tiles!
    continueInstructions: 0
    currentObjective: Get Your Score above 50!
  - orderName: Getting Stunned
    tutorialText:
    - Nice job! Why dont you try expanding as big as possible and see what happens.
    continueInstructions: 0
    currentObjective: Expand as big as you can!
  - orderName: Other Players
    tutorialText:
    - Oof looks like you got stunned by blue player.
    - When stunned you cant do anything for 5 seconds.
    - 'In a real game there will be 3 other players doing the same as you.

'
    - The bigger you expand the more likely it is someone will stun you.
    continueInstructions: 1
    currentObjective: 
  - orderName: Stun
    tutorialText:
    - It looks like blue player is trying to capture some of your tiles!
    - Once tiles are captured another player can easily steal them.
    - Tap on blue player to stop them and get some sweet revenge!
    continueInstructions: 0
    currentObjective: Stun blue player!
  - orderName: Sweet Revenge
    tutorialText:
    - Nice job! notice the timer in the bottom left of the screen.
    - Once you stun another player, you have to wait 12 seconds to use it again.
    - You also can't stun someone while expanding or filling. Try to use your stun
      wisely.
    continueInstructions: 1
    currentObjective: 
  - orderName: Collision
    tutorialText:
    - Uh oh it looks like blue player is trying to capture more tiles.
    - For the sake of this tutorial your stun is now disabled.
    - Dont worry though there is still a way to stop them.
    - When blue player is expanding try expanding your circle next to them until you
      collide.
    continueInstructions: 0
    currentObjective: Collide With Blue Player
  - orderName: Status Bar
    tutorialText:
    - Nice Job! If you collide with another player you'll both be stunned for 5 seconds.
    - Try to use this strategically.
    - If you ever get confused. There is a status bar at the bottom of the screen.
    - It will let you know if youre doing something wrong.
    continueInstructions: 1
    currentObjective: 
  - orderName: End Tutorial
    tutorialText:
    - Congratulations you completed the tutorial!
    - Now you're ready for a real game. Good Luck!
    continueInstructions: 0
